# Student Expense Analyzer

This project is a simple data analysis project where I explored personal expense data using Python.

The goal was to better understand spending habits and practice working with real-world style data.

## What I did

* Loaded and explored the dataset using Pandas
* Cleaned the data (handled types, checked structure)
* Analyzed spending by category and over time
* Created visualizations to better understand the data

## Tools I used

* Python
* Pandas
* Matplotlib

## Dataset

The dataset contains daily expenses such as food, transport, coffee, shopping, and entertainment.

## What I learned

Through this project, I improved my understanding of:

* data cleaning
* grouping and aggregation
* basic data visualization

## How to run

1. Upload the dataset (`expenses.csv`)
2. Run the notebook in Google Colab
